<P>SOME <HI>REMARKABLE PASSAGES</HI> IN THE LIFE OF THE HONOURABLE COL. JAMES GARDINER, Who was &s;lain at the Battle of PRESTON-PANS, <HI>September</HI> 21, 1745.</P>
<P>TO WHICH IS ADDED, THE SERMON Occa&s;ioned by his HEROIC DEATH.</P>
<P>BY P. DODDRIDGE, D.D.</P>
